<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") -%>
<title>How You Help - Baitulmaal</title>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h1 class="text-success">How You Help</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Your donations make a real difference to trusted Baitulmaal agencies.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-success"><i class="fas fa-hands-helping me-2"></i>Support Agencies</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Your contributions directly support verified Baitulmaal agencies serving communities in need. We ensure your donations go to legitimate, verified causes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-success"><i class="fas fa-globe me-2"></i>Impact Beyond Borders</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Donors from around the world can contribute to local and international Baitulmaal organizations, multiplying the global impact of their sadaqah and zakat.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-success"><i class="fas fa-user-shield me-2"></i>Verified Partners</h5>
          <p class="card-text">We take verification seriously. Each Baitulmaal agency is carefully reviewed to ensure authenticity and transparency before appearing on our platform.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-success"><i class="fas fa-heart me-2"></i>Every Rupee Counts</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Whether it's a small sadaqah or a large donation, every contribution helps. You can choose which Baitulmaal agency to support based on your trust and intention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
